trans-unit.source: Specifies information about the size and visibility of the images and label associated with a Ribbon control.

trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [menyfliksområdet Layout och Resizing](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates how to show the image on a control.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger hur du vill visa bilden på en kontroll.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon> control can display a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonImageSize> image, a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonImageSize> image, or the image can be <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonImageSize>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon>kontroll kan visa en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonImageSize>bild, en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonImageSize>bild eller avbildningen kan vara <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonImageSize>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonImageSize> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonImageSize> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonImageSize> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon>

trans-unit.source: If the control does not specify an image of the size that corresponds to the ImageSize setting, no image is displayed.
trans-unit.target: Om kontrollen inte anger en bild av den storlek som motsvarar ImageSize visas ingen bild.
